Pre-Game Insights: Aaron Jones shared his determination to win the game against England, confident that his men will give their best to ensure USA’s T20 World Cup campaign concludes on a positive note.
Captain Aaron Jones considers the match against England important, and shared his desire to win every game when he dons the USA kit, irrespective of who the opponent is.

Jones highlighted the importance of the T20 World Cup campaign in the rise of associate cricket in the USA, mentioning victories against Bangladesh and Pakistan, and close games against India and South Africa.
Jones stated that there is no pressure taking on the defending champions, England, and emphasized the team's belief in their ability to beat any team in the world.
